### 1. 회원가입 완료 알림 (EMAIL + IN_APP)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-welcome-001

{
  "userId": "a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11",
  "notificationType": "ACCOUNT",
  "templateCode": "WELCOME",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "홍길동"
  },
  "channels": ["EMAIL", "IN_APP"],
  "priority": "NORMAL",
  "idempotencyKey": "welcome-user1-20240101"
}

### 2. 결제 완료 알림 (SMS + PUSH + IN_APP)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-payment-001

{
  "userId": "a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11",
  "notificationType": "TRANSACTION",
  "templateCode": "PAYMENT_COMPLETE",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "홍길동",
    "amount": "50000",
    "orderId": "ORD-2024-001"
  },
  "channels": ["SMS", "PUSH", "IN_APP"],
  "priority": "NORMAL",
  "idempotencyKey": "payment-ord2024001"
}

### 3. 보안 경고 알림 (HIGH priority - quiet hours 무시)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-security-001

{
  "userId": "a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11",
  "notificationType": "SECURITY",
  "templateCode": "SECURITY_ALERT",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "홍길동",
    "alertMessage": "새로운 기기에서 로그인이 감지되었습니다."
  },
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "idempotencyKey": "security-alert-001"
}

### 4. 마케팅 알림 (수신 동의 확인 + quiet hours 적용)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: corr-marketing-001

{
  "userId": "a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11",
  "notificationType": "MARKETING",
  "templateCode": "MARKETING_PROMO",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "홍길동",
    "promoTitle": "봄맞이 특별 할인",
    "promoDescription": "전 상품 30% 할인 이벤트!"
  },
  "channels": ["EMAIL", "PUSH", "IN_APP"],
  "priority": "LOW",
  "idempotencyKey": "marketing-spring-2024"
}

### 5. 마케팅 알림 - 수신 거부 사용자 (차단됨)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "b0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a22",
  "notificationType": "MARKETING",
  "templateCode": "MARKETING_PROMO",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "김철수",
    "promoTitle": "봄맞이 특별 할인",
    "promoDescription": "전 상품 30% 할인 이벤트!"
  },
  "channels": ["EMAIL", "PUSH"],
  "idempotencyKey": "marketing-blocked-user2"
}

### 6. 동일 idempotency key 중복 요청 (첫 번째 결과 반환)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11",
  "notificationType": "ACCOUNT",
  "templateCode": "WELCOME",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "홍길동"
  },
  "idempotencyKey": "welcome-user1-20240101"
}

### 7. Provider 실패 테스트 (fail@example.com -> permanent failure)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "c0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a33",
  "notificationType": "ACCOUNT",
  "templateCode": "WELCOME",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "실패테스트"
  },
  "channels": ["EMAIL"],
  "idempotencyKey": "fail-email-test-001"
}

### 8. 알림 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. 사용자 In-App 알림 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11/in-app-notifications?limit=50&offset=0

### 10. In-App 알림 읽음 처리
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11/in-app-notifications/{{inAppNotificationId}}/read
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. 사용자 알림 설정 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11/preferences

### 12. 사용자 알림 설정 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/a0eebc99-9c0b-4ef8-bb6d-6bb9bd380a11/preferences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "preferences": [
    {
      "notificationType": "MARKETING",
      "channel": "EMAIL",
      "enabled": true,
      "quietHoursEnabled": true,
      "quietHoursStart": "22:00",
      "quietHoursEnd": "08:00"
    },
    {
      "notificationType": "MARKETING",
      "channel": "PUSH",
      "enabled": false,
      "quietHoursEnabled": false
    }
  ]
}

### 13. 템플릿 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/templates/WELCOME

### 14. 템플릿 렌더링 미리보기
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/templates/WELCOME/render-preview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "variables": {
    "userName": "테스트사용자"
  }
}

### 15. 헬스 체크
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
